Privacy Policy for Street Sport Manager

Effective Date: February 17, 2026

Street Sport Manager (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our mobile application (“App”).

1. Information We Collect

When you use Street Sport Manager, we may collect the following types of information:

1.1 Personal Information

Name

Email address (if provided for account creation or notifications)

Optional profile information such as player rating

1.2 Game and Group Data

Group names and passwords

Match schedules, locations, and results

Team compositions and player participation

1.3 Device and Usage Information

Device type and operating system

App usage data (e.g., number of games created, registration activity)

Crash reports and analytics data to improve the app

2. How We Use Your Information

We use the collected information to:

Provide and manage your account and groups

Organize matches, balance teams, and manage registrations

Display game results and updated league standings

Improve the app experience and fix technical issues

Send optional notifications about matches, registrations, and updates

3. Sharing Your Information

We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information only in the following circumstances:

With other users of your group (e.g., names displayed in the group or team)

With service providers that help us operate the App (e.g., cloud hosting)

If required by law or to protect our legal rights

4. Your Choices

You can choose not to provide optional profile information.

You can leave a group at any time, which removes your data from that group.

You can delete your account by contacting us at the email below.

5. Data Retention

We retain your information only as long as necessary to provide the App and comply with legal obligations. When you delete your account or leave a group, your personal data will be removed from our servers.

6. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or modification. However, no system is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

7. Children’s Privacy

Street Sport Manager is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted in the App and take effect immediately. Please check this page periodically for updates.

9. Contact Us

If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:

Email: lirazhad@gmail.com
